{"tid":2228960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"管浩鳴：台灣律師明與當局見面　陳同佳投案意願無問題","createTime":"2020-10-04T04:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T04:44:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bc9dde81c0441d8a43fb63aac60cef90b14c6802","tid":2228960,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T04:33:51.000Z","msg":"在台灣，陸委會批評，特區政府提供協助台灣殺人案疑犯陳同佳赴台一事，近一年依然無所作為，強調案件關鍵在於陳同佳真實投案意願，以及特區政府的責任感，呼籲雙方都拿回初心，用具體行動，透過窗口與台方聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n協助陳同佳的聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴表示，台灣律師明天與相關法律部門見面後，事件會更明朗，強調陳同佳的投案意願無問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552966-20201004.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552966-20201004.htm&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdn4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=bd48090b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552966-20201004.htm&h=69ef1072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552966-20201004.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d729bf9225e6ad8416a3a5cb39082993546a5223","tid":2228960,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T04:35:16.000Z","msg":"意願得 係 一係唔係。咩撚野叫無問題"},{"pid":"eaf06324378eb33b1654178b47bb3cc4ee2cb22d","tid":2228960,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"總之我會去，某年十月！"},{"pid":"2a075e7ec65d2829685960852a0f71a9dbc5d9dd","tid":2228960,"uid":370972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T04:37:12.000Z","msg":"入台紙係咪仲valid 先？"},{"pid":"86749d77f5101b9abcda514f02ce648fb18ca444","tid":2228960,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"咩叫無問題<br />\n<br />\n咁yes定no先"},{"pid":"9e5fb6ee0b0131540dec38da876bf21ab8ebe4da","tid":2228960,"uid":379077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"我想投案架 但ps5仲未玩夠<img src=\"/as